WEBVTT

1
00:00:16.366 --> 00:00:17.433
Be careful

2
00:00:19.566 --> 00:00:21.200
I came to see you

3
00:00:26.133 --> 00:00:27.300
How is Xiaoxi?

4
00:00:27.366 --> 00:00:28.366
Life has been saved

5
00:00:28.366 --> 00:00:29.200
But

6
00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:30.966
Your child is gone

7
00:00:30.966 --> 00:00:32.466
And now he's in a vegetative state.

8
00:00:32.466 --> 00:00:34.233
I don't know when I'll wake up

9
00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:35.866
Why is this happening?

10
00:00:35.866 --> 00:00:37.800
