11
00:00:43.533 --> 00:00:44.566
Thanks to me.

12
00:00:44.866 --> 00:00:46.666
If it weren't for my failure to protect her

13
00:00:46.666 --> 00:00:47.666
Neither will

14
00:00:50.266 --> 00:00:51.500
You left with one hand.

15
00:00:51.533 --> 00:00:53.400
It's not bad to be able to save your life

16
00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:54.933
You can take care of him at the end

17
00:00:54.933 --> 00:00:56.166
Talk to him

18
00:00:56.533 --> 00:00:58.033
Maybe wake up

19
00:01:01.666 --> 00:01:02.466
Creek

20
00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:04.800
Open your eyes and see if I'm okay

21
00:01:04.800 --> 00:01:06.233
I know wrong

22
00:01:06.266 --> 00:01:07.466
Wake up quickly

23
00:01:07.466 --> 00:01:09.200
You can ask me to do anything

24
